RebelYell's dead body had been lying unnoticed just a
few hundred feet from the battlefield for some time.It
was lying there, covered in mech fluid from the fatal
wounds RebelYell had recieved.Then the Matrix reached
out to it. The body began to glow, and its limbs began
to convulse. Its wounds began to heal.It was made
stronger, twice as strong as before. Then, a spark was
downloaded into its empty chest cavity.
